Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:29.67,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is there no final{\i}\N{\i1}piece to unravel this puzzle?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:36.97,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wander around the search area with dread{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:44.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With shaky self-confidence{\i}\N{\i1}facing unyielding damnation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:48.31,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still alive, but I can't catch up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:54.53,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to residual images of hidden memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:58.74,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let loose dark shame unbounded{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:02.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the ends of this world of kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:06.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even hopes best forgotten are silenced{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:10.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as corruption spreads out before our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:13.59,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consign it to darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:17.30,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ego on trial{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:28.48,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a moment of hesitation is seen ecstasy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.98,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord6\be6}"Episode 9: 'Stopped Time'"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:36.61,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Maximum Clearance 2.5m"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosions? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any details yet.\NJust that some powerful explosives
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,were used in several\Nlocations within the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanda...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop Hitomi. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He abducts the Prime Minister,\Nand now, terrorist bombings...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Currently, the confirmed\Ncasualty count alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}from these bombings is twelve dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:15.28,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\fs108\bord7.5\be8\pos(960,990)}Bombings within the city leave many dead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}twenty-four seriously injured,\Nwith four people reported missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The explosions took place\Nduring the evening rush hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and it is anticipated\Nthat the toll in human lives
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}will continue to rise hereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. "Toll."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's terrible what is happening, is it not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,More worried about others\Nthan yourself. That's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're enjoying yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We were discussing\NMiss Sakurakoji's character.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd actually bring her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My role is to cater to whatever you seek, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it has always been, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been under\Nguard for a long time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Under guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,First, there was Heike,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then, more recently, Ogami was\Ntransferred to that school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep you guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, Ogami didn't\Nseem to be aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it done to try to thwart my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You were awfully well-prepared,\Nbut I still prevailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Plans? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a rarebreed, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to keep you secured here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,since you'd be a\Nproblem if you got in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do\Nis sit back and watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,without interfering with my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Casualties continue to\Nrise after series of explosions"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean these explosions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I said it was to save the\NCode: Breakers, would you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you must have some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your level of\Nkindness better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.07,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,120)\pos(1093.5,834)\frz14.21}Received 1 new message
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.03,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,50)\fs84\bord7.5\be8\an7\frz13.67\pos(621,460.5)}Subj: Hitomi's location\N\NFrom: Adam's friend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, it's Kanda. I got a text\Nfrom an unknown sender
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that shows Hitomi's\Ncurrent location, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i} got it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, Ace, the bombs\Nthat were set around the city
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't the end of this, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The real plan is just getting started, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How obnoxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you've been\Nsniffing around, huh, Heike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound so sordid. I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's not as though\NI trust you 100 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of tricks did you\Npull to find this hideout so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you've been keeping an\Neye on me since before this began.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My information network\Nhad this location marked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just reached the end of your rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}is{\i} alarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have figured out\Nwhat your true intention is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to have you be\Ncaught by Eden. I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is precisely why\NI abducted Miss Sakurakoji,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and reduced Hachoji Rui\Nto a bloody mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You, who cares more than\Nanyone for the Code: Breakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,took out Oji? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I understand your anger\Nand grief more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you hurt Oji?!\NYou'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not know the feelings\Nof someone who does not exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, I don't blame you\Nfor not believing me. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you please. But, if you try\Nanything funny, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I will endeavor to\Nlive up to your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kanda is here now, that\Nmeans that Ogami will be along soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, a conflict is unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is sudden, but Heike,\Nwould you do a job for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop Hitomi. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to tie you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:30.05,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Emergency report"\N"Series of bombings"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, isn't Sakura with you?\NShe hasn't come home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not answering her cell, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Could something have happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I think I know where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you if I find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Number six!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Number two has turned on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Number six!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yuki, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to Number five?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb! I saw the whole thing!\NYou attacked Number five!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That was careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Heike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it means!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you really have\Nturned on us, huh, Number two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be a pain how the\Nsound special ability is invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you can get a handle\Non its straight-line movement,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not difficult to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah, you're pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well of course I'm going to evade them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No mercy, I see, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who stand in my\Nway don't require any mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to stick to that policy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Number six! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep heading on up, Number six.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of Number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Then I will dispose of you, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanda, wasn't Hitomi here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Hitomi got you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami! Miss Kanda is being controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You must help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, you send out\Nelectrical commands to her brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and control her with them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not hard at all. Much easier\Nthan controlling a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Master... Hitomi has me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, please get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How many more rounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take all the bullets you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and empty the clip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, I think I'm going\Nto take you out of the picture here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have given instructions to Kanda
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that her final shot is\Nto go through her own head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do? If you avoid\Nher shots, Kanda will keep shooting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and with the last bullet,\Nshe will commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if you take a bullet, and die,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,my control over Kanda will end right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanda will not have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you look on as Kanda kills herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is beyond dastardly, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a kindhearted girl you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, you used to be friends\Nwith Miss Kanda and Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do something this mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away with this, Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will end this, by my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami... you don't mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Striking back and eliminating an\Nenemy who threatens you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,without any hesitation.\NYou haven't changed, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But, can you really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Master... I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, wait! Don't do it, Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What on earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? You loosened the ropes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! You are back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your desperate wish broke\Nyou free of Hitomi's special ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a rarebreed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, you seem\Nlikely to interfere in all sort of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you intend to take Puppy hostage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, what are you scheming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The old you was not someone who\Nwould do this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still not know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,even after looking at the clocks in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...has nothing but stopped clocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the times of the\NCode: Breakers' deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,6:23... the former Code 03\Ndies while on escort duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,22:47... the former Code 06\Ndies in a sudden accident
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,while passing judgment on evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who do not exist do not\Neven get headstones erected to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's the least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They all died judging evil\Nthat the law could not judge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,without anyone knowing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing...\Nhas to be brought to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing this for his\Nfriends that have died, all by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who gave them\Ntheir orders was the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For this, he must pay.\NI will have the Prime Minister
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,accept the consequences with his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, you can't go killing the Prime Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will come of\Nyou doing something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, something will come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prime Minister will die\Nwhile performing in his supreme role.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His supreme role?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an explosion,\Njust now! The smoke is tremendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Many people are down. It's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Many people will die before\Nthe Prime Minister's execution.\N- Many people are down. It's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Many people will die before\Nthe Prime Minister's execution.\N- the situation is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The citizenry must be in terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then finally comes the main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prime Minister, along with\Neven more people across Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,will lose their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For what reason are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing people who are without any guilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To leave this memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To ingrain terror within the memories
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of the people of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality that many people are being executed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,together with Prime Minister Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They should learn their lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who live in a world\Nof fabricated, temporary peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a temporary, fabricated peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!\NMy child! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People who bask\Nin peace will tremble in fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then, from the bottom of their hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they will want someone to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,whomever brought about\Nthis kind of atrocity for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An absolute "someone,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who will eliminate evil,\Nno matter the means.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Code: Breakers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing so, the Code: Breakers\Nwill no longer have to die
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,without anyone knowing about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the Code: Breakers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- But!\N- So when all of this is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll come forward as\Na Code: Breaker of Justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and judge evil, out in the open?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, I'm not comfortable\Nbeing a kept dog of Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind moving out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,By creating this much of a stink,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden might think so, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join me, Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But do not forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Code: Breakers who\Njudge evil are still killers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to reward that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you get it, Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed people who are\Ninnocent to bring about this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You! The one who most\Nhated when innocent people died!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the best you've got, Yuki?\NWhat a spoilsport.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting warmed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, I've gotta\Nhand it to Number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed, Ogami.\NBut there's no turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time for\NCode: Breakers to start to exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No longer as those who die\Nin solitude, unknown to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone can be who they wish to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With this sacrifice of the citizenry's terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I liberate the Code: Breakers from Eden!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukihina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I was wondering what\Nwas taking you so long to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have just\Ngone on ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for you\Nto be wrapped up in this, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Yukihina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot melt my ice with your flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Yukihina, I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Ogami?\NPutting Sakura in danger, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sakura! The star has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the hero has to come in late, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hold it! Give back the Prime Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you right now,\Nthere are bombs in this building, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting out immediately\Nwould be good for your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Give his papa,\Nthe Prime Minster, back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, the fight is on hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Who would have thought\Nyou'd come along with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you kill the Prime Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor shall I allow you to kill anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what took place in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:22:01.55,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you, too, will know{\i}\N{\i1}where that white crow is heading{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:07.22,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We fly through the brilliant city,{\i}\N{\i1}unnoticed by all around{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:21.73,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking only for a reason to live{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:27.15,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ashamed of our hollow selves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:31.91,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should we just laugh and go along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:37.54,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rules the world has decided on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:42.29,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stripped bare, following{\i}\N{\i1}wherever our instincts lead{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:46.34,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the truth from{\i}\N{\i1}which we've averted our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:50.97,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Verdicts handed down for no one's sake{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:55.77,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cast off the dark robes and get on your feet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:00.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure white wishes become our wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:05.28,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shake off your hesitations now, and fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:13.74,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have no fear; the answers{\i}\N{\i1}lie beyond the darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, the night the city was choked
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with the smell of death and gun smoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is when I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time,\N"Code: Breaker" episode 10,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"The World People See."
